---
title: Sweet-Soy White Fish & Garlic Rice with Garlic Greens & Crispy Shallots
description: We’ve finally spotted the ultimate fish dish on the horizon. These dory fish fillets will crumble in your mouth and calm stormy
seas when seasoned in sweet and soy flavours. It’s all steam ahead when you get a taste of the ginger veggies with a hint of
honey and soy. Drop the anchor, it’s time to eat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65030d83ddf45550bcf9f3c7-e935aa05.jpeg
